title: Julio Iglesias - My Life - The Greatest Hits 1998 musicfromrizzo
description:
I was first introduced to this great music from the great Julio Iglesias by my sister
and brother-in-law Jose (who is from Chile) decades ago now. They both love his
music and are never far from listening to it again at every opportunity I found
and so it was for me too back then, and I've never stopped loving his great music.

One of my most favourite songs is on this CD set ("Caruso" - also done by Andrea Bocelli and Luciano Pavarotti along the way) and as well I am glad to find old spanish favourites on here that are Julio Iglesias standard numbers through these many years now. We also have the 1.5GB musicfromrizzo Julio Iglesias collection posted at this site for you, and we had half a dozen seeds at one point today, when I checked. gracias!

please seed this great music for the family and all the planet -
Julio has lots of money and doesnt need more - the family needs
great music to keep our spirits up, and we'll take care of our own
some other way than charging for music so many times over.

thanks indeed - gracias to the family in Spain Chile Argentina Mexico etc

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
